## Third-Party Components

This project includes third-party software components. Full license texts for NVIDIA CUDA/cuDNN, Intel OpenVINO, OneTBB, OneDNN, and OpenCV are included in the installation directory under the "Third party licenses" folder.

* FFmpeg: This software uses libraries from the FFmpeg project (http://ffmpeg.org) licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License (LGPL) v2.1. The precompiled FFmpeg binaries distributed with this software were compiled by the OpenCV project. The source code can be found at: https://github.com/opencv/opencv_3rdparty/tree/ffmpeg/master. The creator of this software does not claim ownership over FFmpeg.